    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="hexo-d报错"><a href="#hexo-d报错" class="headerlink" title="hexo d报错"></a>hexo d报错</h3><p>原因：<br>问题大多是因为git进行push或者hexo d的时候改变了一些.deploy_git文件下的内容。</p><p>解决办法：<br>删除.deploy_git文件夹;</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">输入git config --global core.autocrlf false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后，依次执行：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;hexo-d报错&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#hexo-d报错&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;hexo d报错&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;hexo d报错&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;原因：&lt;br&gt;问题大多是因为git进行push或者hexo d的时候改变了一些.deploy</summary>
      
    
    
    
